Interface Variable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CallableSBase, Cloneable, NamedSBase, NamedSBaseWithDerivedUnit, Quantity, SBase, SBaseWithDerivedUnit, Serializable, TreeNode, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport, UniqueNamedSBase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Compartment, Parameter, Species, SpeciesReference, Symbol

    public interface Variable
extends Quantity, UniqueNamedSBase
    A variable of the system is a Quantity whose value may change during a simulation. To decide whether it has to stay constant, this interface provides the necessary methods.
    Since:
    0.8
    Version:
